    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like no matter what i do it doesn't matter. i try to be happy and i try to find my community but the hate and the constant exhaustion... it's just so much. feels like i'm just running a race that has no finish line and everyone is just waiting for me to trip. i'm just so done with feeling like a mistake all the time.",
