      "content": "i get what you're saying but it just feels so performative. like, \"reach out to a therapist\" or \"you're valuable\"... it doesn't change the reality that the world is built to reject me. it's just a cycle of pain. sometimes i look at it and it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the struggle is to just... stop. like, maybe there's just no way for someone like me to ever actually have peace in this life.",
